{"type":"message","id":"52983bb7","parentId":"397c17b8","timestamp":"2026-02-25T03:42:33.389Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me provide the user with a summary of command-line search options.","thinkingSignature":"5bc57dba74f6dab7c93772642173c4cda538f93a65ac4e8cda44aae48b5bd14c"},{"type":"text","text":"**当前可用的命令行搜索方案：**\n\n| 工具 | 安装 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `ddgs` (DuckDuckGo) | `pip install ddgs` | ✅ 已装，但可能被限制 |\n| `googler` | `apt install googler` | 未安装 |\n| `ddg` | `pip install ddg` | 已安装但 Python 2 语法不兼容 |\n\n**更实用的替代方案：**\n\n1. **使用 Bing/Google HTML 搜索** (通过 curl)\n2. **配置 Brave Search API** - 最稳定可靠\n3. **浏览器模式** - 你打开网页，我来读取\n\n目前环境网络可能对 DDG API 有限制。如果你希望继续尝试完整20条/板块新闻，最实用的方案是：\n\n```bash\n# 配置 Brave Search API（免费 2000次/月）\nopenclaw configure --section web\n```\n\n或者你可以每天手动打开财经网站，我来帮你抓取内容。需要我继续用当前方式（web_fetch 逐页抓取）收集更多新闻吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":62318,"output":238,"cacheRead":11401,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73957,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771990945313}}
