{"type":"message","id":"d55c516e","parentId":"4291c8b7","timestamp":"2026-02-25T06:33:05.875Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so web_fetch can reach yicai.com. The issue is that the search engines are blocking our requests. Let me think of a practical solution for the user.\n\nGiven the constraints:\n1. Headless server - no browser\n2. No credit card for Brave API\n3. Search engines blocking curl requests\n\nThe most practical solution might be to:\n1. Use a simple RSS feed reader if available\n2. Or use a different approach - scrape specific news site pages directly\n\nLet me try to find some RSS feeds or news APIs that work.","thinkingSignature":"655812246114617925244a48a402cb1274ab1684749ec2ee4089d5582a959509"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_i8yxwnwj9k8f_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Try different news APIs/endpoints\ncurl -s --connect-timeout 10 \"https://www.yicai.com/news/ajax/newslistById?id=103057\" 2>&1 | head -50"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":63582,"output":182,"cacheRead":11320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75084,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772001178636}}
{"type":"message","id":"8e8a1623","parentId":"d55c516e","timestamp":"2026-02-25T06:33:08.369Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_i8yxwnwj9k8f_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<!DOCTYPE html><html><head> <script src=\"/assets/yc_autologin.js\"></script><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge,chrome=1\"><link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\"><meta name=\"description\" content=\"第一财经官方网站，7X24小时提供股市行情、经济大势、金融政策、行业动态、专家分析等财经资讯；全网独家直播谈股论金、今日股市、公司与行业、解码财商、头脑风暴等第一财经电视节目。\"><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"第一财经,第一财经日报,第一财经周刊,第一财经电视,第一财经在线直播,股票,股市,创业板,中小板,新三板,黄金,GDP,投资,理财,金融,商业\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/assets/jquery.min.js\"></script><script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-BW57C8STG3\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\">var _pb = _pb || [];    var _hmt = _hmt || [];    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}    gtag('js', new Date());    gtag('config', 'G-BW57C8STG3');</script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/assets/crypto-js.min.js\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/assets/Fingerprint2.js\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://o.alicdn.com/captcha-frontend/aliyunCaptcha/AliyunCaptcha.js\"></script> <title>页面不存在</title><link href=\"/css/404.css?27cc9060a1236ba23bea\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/js/common.js?27cc9060a1236ba23bea\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/js/404.js?27cc9060a1236ba23bea\"></script></head><body><div class=\"g-doc\"> <div class=\"g-hd\" id=\"pcHeader\"></div> <div class=\"g-bd\"><div class=\"m-error\"><img src=\"/img/index_55.66e5c0f4.png\"></div></div> <div class=\"g-ft\" id=\"gocFt\"></div></div></body></html>"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2481,"aggregated":"<!DOCTYPE html><html><head> <script src=\"/assets/yc_autologin.js\"></script><meta charset=\"UTF-8\"><meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge,chrome=1\"><link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\"><meta name=\"description\" content=\"第一财经官方网站，7X24小时提供股市行情、经济大势、金融政策、行业动态、专家分析等财经资讯；全网独家直播谈股论金、今日股市、公司与行业、解码财商、头脑风暴等第一财经电视节目。\"><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"第一财经,第一财经日报,第一财经周刊,第一财经电视,第一财经在线直播,股票,股市,创业板,中小板,新三板,黄金,GDP,投资,理财,金融,商业\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/assets/jquery.min.js\"></script><script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-BW57C8STG3\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\">var _pb = _pb || [];    var _hmt = _hmt || [];    window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];    function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}    gtag('js', new Date());    gtag('config', 'G-BW57C8STG3');</script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/assets/crypto-js.min.js\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/assets/Fingerprint2.js\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"https://o.alicdn.com/captcha-frontend/aliyunCaptcha/AliyunCaptcha.js\"></script> <title>页面不存在</title><link href=\"/css/404.css?27cc9060a1236ba23bea\" rel=\"stylesheet\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/js/common.js?27cc9060a1236ba23bea\"></script><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/js/404.js?27cc9060a1236ba23bea\"></script></head><body><div class=\"g-doc\"> <div class=\"g-hd\" id=\"pcHeader\"></div> <div class=\"g-bd\"><div class=\"m-error\"><img src=\"/img/index_55.66e5c0f4.png\"></div></div> <div class=\"g-ft\" id=\"gocFt\"></div></div></body></html>","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772001188362}}
{"type":"message","id":"0c93443a","parentId":"8e8a1623","timestamp":"2026-02-25T06:33:21.096Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The specific AJAX endpoint doesn't work. Let me try another approach - maybe finding a public financial news API or RSS feed that works.Actually, let me think about this differently. The user wants to collect stock news regularly. Even without search APIs, we could:\n\n1. Use web_fetch to directly scrape specific news pages (like I did earlier)\n2. Or use a cron job with specific URLs\n\nThe limitation is that we can only get what we can directly fetch from news sites. The current approach of using web_fetch on specific article pages does work.\n\nLet me give the user a practical summary of what works and what doesn't in this environment.","thinkingSignature":"d4b9762cf7e622bcc00ed6a552bb1996d387bac261a15dba61a445d773a134d5"},{"type":"text","text":"实测发现 Bing/Google HTML 搜索在这个服务器环境里**基本不可用** - 搜索请求被阻止或返回空。\n\n**当前环境可行的方案：**\n\n| 方案 | 可用性 |\n|------|--------|\n| ✅ web_fetch 直接抓取财经文章 | 可用（已测试） |\n| ❌ Bing/Google HTML 搜索 | 被屏蔽 |\n| ❌ DuckDuckGo API | 被限制 |\n| ❌ Brave Search API | 需要银行卡 |\n| ❌ RSS feeds | 大部分不可用 |\n\n**最实际的替代方案：**\n\n既然 web_fetch 可以直接读取文章页面，你可以：\n\n1. **维护一个固定的新闻源 URL 列表** - 每天抓取这些页面的热点新闻\n2. **用 cron 定时任务** + 我帮你写的脚本\n\n例如可以抓取的页面：\n- `https://www.yicai.com/news/` (第一财经首页)\n- `https://www.eastmoney.com/` (东方财富)\n- 特定板块文章页面\n\n**你想要我帮你写一个脚本吗？** \n- 可以每天定时从这几个固定来源抓取热点新闻\n- 不需要搜索 API，直接抓取页面内容\n- 适合服务器环境运行"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":64306,"output":380,"cacheRead":11320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":76006,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772001188369}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2ee7dab","parentId":"0c93443a","timestamp":"2026-02-25T06:33:21.296Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"fc780cfa-87ec-4b40-a6a9-432cdc461635\",\n  \"sender\": \"gateway-client\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-02-25 14:32 GMT+8] 已上方案不太适合我，当前安装在Linux-debian无界面的服务器发行版里，所以使用浏览器不合适，配置brave search api我也没有银行卡可以绑定，使用bing/google html搜索会不会效果不行"}],"timestamp":1772001201284}}
{"type":"message","id":"5c28eea9","parentId":"f2ee7dab","timestamp":"2026-02-25T06:33:34.188Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about using Bing/Google HTML search on their headless Debian server. They want to know if it will work. Let me test it more thoroughly.","thinkingSignature":"8f553156cf8bf397f7e9584e27d344bd27c996e701692cfc2ebe222cd0b03fc6"},{"type":"text","text":"让我再测试一下 Bing/Google HTML 搜索的实际效果：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_for1vn9s7yd1_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Test Bing with different approach\ncurl -s \"https://www.bing.com/search?q=stock+market+news+china\" \\\n  -H \"User-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/120.0.0.0 Safari/537.36\" \\\n  -H \"Accept: text/html,application/xhtml+xml\" \\\n  -H \"Accept-Language: en-US,en;q=0.9\" \\\n  2>&1 | grep -i \"title\\|href\" | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":211,"cacheRead":5733,"cacheWrite":69775,"totalTokens":75747,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772001201294}}
