{"type":"message","id":"fa28cadc","parentId":"88154a44","timestamp":"2026-02-25T13:14:42.325Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_uxbmvn9ltca3_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.2.24 (df9a474) — curl for conversations.\n\nUsage: openclaw message [options] [command]\n\nSend, read, and manage messages and channel actions\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help   Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  ban          Ban a member\n  broadcast    Broadcast a message to multiple targets\n  channel      Channel actions\n  delete       Delete a message\n  edit         Edit a message\n  emoji        Emoji actions\n  event        Event actions\n  kick         Kick a member\n  member       Member actions\n  permissions  Fetch channel permissions\n  pin          Pin a message\n  pins         List pinned messages\n  poll         Send a poll\n  react        Add or remove a reaction\n  reactions    List reactions on a message\n  read         Read recent messages\n  role         Role actions\n  search       Search Discord messages\n  send         Send a message"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2852,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.2.24 (df9a474) — curl for conversations.\n\nUsage: openclaw message [options] [command]\n\nSend, read, and manage messages and channel actions\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help   Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  ban          Ban a member\n  broadcast    Broadcast a message to multiple targets\n  channel      Channel actions\n  delete       Delete a message\n  edit         Edit a message\n  emoji        Emoji actions\n  event        Event actions\n  kick         Kick a member\n  member       Member actions\n  permissions  Fetch channel permissions\n  pin          Pin a message\n  pins         List pinned messages\n  poll         Send a poll\n  react        Add or remove a reaction\n  reactions    List reactions on a message\n  read         Read recent messages\n  role         Role actio