{"type":"message","id":"028e003e","parentId":"bafefb42","timestamp":"2026-02-25T13:51:16.360Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_cruyx80fxt9s_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.2.24 (df9a474) — Your .env is showing; don't worry, I'll pretend I didn't see it.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":5402,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.2.24 (df9a474) — Your .env is showing; don't worry, I'll pretend I didn't see it.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772027476353}}
{"type":"message","id":"e93b1ad7","parentId":"028e003e","timestamp":"2026-02-25T13:51:25.194Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the cron add command to see how to create a daily task.","thinkingSignature":"f99769a7102978e32e2e67156fbaafea839755a00bef02e2e22b9c5aa02720c8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l9y84cec7qzq_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --help 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":122839,"output":51,"cacheRead":11481,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":134371,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772027476361}}
{"type":"message","id":"37a10f87","parentId":"e93b1ad7","timestamp":"2026-02-25T13:51:28.677Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_l9y84cec7qzq_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.2.24 (df9a474) — We ship features faster than Apple ships calculator updates.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3463,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.2.24 (df9a474) — We ship features faster than Apple ships calculator updates.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772027488663}}
{"type":"message","id":"124e0521","parentId":"37a10f87","timestamp":"2026-02-25T13:51:38.765Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can create a cron job to run daily at 9:00 AM. The cron expression for daily at 9:00 AM would be \"0 9 * * *\". Let me create the cron job with the message that triggers the stock news collection.","thinkingSignature":"d2d59d3bdb0dd6c25d812ec24ac07b5e4e042790171a55849a9482987fdb5230"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7qtqb6vujtr7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"每日股市新闻汇总\" \\\n  --cron \"0 9 * * *\" \\\n  --tz \"Asia/Shanghai\" \\\n  --message \"帮我收集过去一天（current_time-24h）股市相关的热门新闻，遵循以下规则：1. 按板块分类每个板块20条新闻，包括的板块有：- AI/机器人板块 - A股昨日热门板块 - 美股昨日热门板块 2. 回答的消息格式必须展示以下信息：- 完整标题+发布来源(格式：[标题]-[来源]) - 文章内容简写（100字左右） - 原文链接 3. 新闻发布来源包括但不限于：- 东方财富网:https://finance.eastmoney.com/ - 第一财经:https://www.yicai.com/news/ - 新浪财经:https://finance.sina.com.cn/ - 中国经济网:http://finance.ce.cn/ - 财新网:https://deepview.caixin.com - 证券时报网:https://www.stcn.com/article/list/yw.html - 经济观察网:https://www.eeo.com.cn/kuaixun/ - 界面新闻:https://www.jiemian.com/lists/1324kb.html - 金融界:https://24h.jrj.com.cn/newsFlash - 同花顺财经:https://news.10jqka.com.cn/realtimenews.html 4. 抓取方式：- 在3中提到的网址（随机，至少抓取3个源，要求各个来源占比平衡），通过站内页面抓取资讯，不使用搜索 - 并实现多源的去重 5. 发送方式：telegram\" \\\n  --channel telegram \\\n  --to \"5889732065\" \\\n  --expect-final \\\n  --timeout-seconds 300"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":123498,"output":455,"cacheRead":11481,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":135434,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772027488680}}
