{"type":"message","id":"ba3c6177","parentId":"9f25f501","timestamp":"2026-02-25T16:30:28.567Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking what the thinking level determines. Let me explain what the thinking level controls in OpenClaw.","thinkingSignature":"4d59c7ac31aff3f2af71727147dcd246bb9bfbbcb7bb264d909dc03ade39d567"},{"type":"text","text":"**Thinking 等级决定什么：**\n\n| 等级 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **off** | 完全不启用思考模式，响应最快 |\n| **minimal** | 最小思考，仅处理最基本推理 |\n| **low** | 低级思考，简单任务使用 |\n| **medium** | 中级思考，平衡速度和深度 |\n| **high** | 高级思考，最深入的分析，适合复杂问题 |\n\n**主要影响：**\n- **响应速度**：越低越快\n- **分析深度**：越高越深入\n- **Token消耗**：越高消耗越多\n- **适用场景**：\n  - off/low：简单问答、查天气\n  - medium：一般任务、写作\n  - high：复杂推理、代码调试\n\n你当前是 **off**，想调整到哪个等级？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":195,"cacheRead":138426,"cacheWrite":375,"totalTokens":139024,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772037020995}}
