{"type":"message","id":"c54c176e","parentId":"9c3271ec","timestamp":"2026-02-25T16:47:21.437Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The WhatsApp target needs to be an E.164 number. Let me ask the user what their WhatsApp number is or check if there's a default configured.","thinkingSignature":"ff0f55e42e78e277facab4706974ce116bda1adb8e10d35f82b78d030d287f4d"},{"type":"text","text":"WhatsApp 需要目标号码（E.164格式），请问你的 WhatsApp 号码是多少？\n\n例如：`+86 138 0000 0000`\n\n或者你可以先确认 WhatsApp 是否已配置好：\n```bash\nopenclaw status\n```"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":98646,"output":87,"cacheRead":11481,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110214,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772038017207}}
