{"type":"message","id":"db02427c","parentId":"3e9adbaa","timestamp":"2026-02-26T09:35:26.139Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says they didn't receive the email. Let me check a few things:\n\n1. Check if the emails were actually sent - they show success in SMTP\n2. Check Gmail sent folder or spam folder\n3. The recipient might be going to spam or being rejected\n\nLet me check if there are any issues with the email delivery.","thinkingSignature":"617dde66f7cfc8330eb606cce4732aa52c510346996cbdc650917e40cb25aa0d"},{"type":"text","text":"你好！\n\n邮件显示发送成功但没收到，可能是以下原因：\n\n1. **垃圾邮件** - 检查垃圾邮件文件夹\n2. **Gmail 发送限制** - 你的 Gmail 可能限制了自动发送\n3. **收件地址问题** - 确认 wangqining@myhexin.com 是否正确\n\n让我检查一下 Gmail 的发送设置：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yjqmsq1u6ena_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# Check Gmail IMAP to see if sent emails are there\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/imap-smtp-email && node scripts/imap.js check --limit 5 --mailbox \"Sent\" 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":28,"output":214,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":146723,"totalTokens":146965,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772098509308}}
